textBox.richText: Check chedda like a food inspecta’, here is my first blog: So I have been a little behind on these blog entries. Im sorry, this is all new for me. Our first spiel has come and gone and we have had some success - we won! In the Pitaburrow we met Ed’s mom; she is a French riot, just like the ones in Montreal when the Canadiens score a goal. She Hooked us up with some fine cooking, but would not let us stop eating.. Had two run-ins with the U of Ottawa girls soccer team and soccer has never looked so appealing. Whoever invented LuLu lemon is okay in my books. After winning, Andy, Ed, Willburforce and I each got a Wendy’s frosty... While Brandon took a 1am bus ride back to Ottawa. He rolled in to the capitol just around 6am for his morning class. Back in “the loo,” we all woke up to news that a twenty-year old was stabbed on a greyhound that night... YIKES! We weren’t too concerned because he is just the lead, but imagine if it was me!
